      • DEFAULT_HTTP_COOKIE_MANAGER_PROPERTY

        public static final DefaultHttpCookieManagerProperty DEFAULT_HTTP_COOKIE_MANAGER_PROPERTY
        This instance reads value of the property 'default.http.cookie.handler' and returns a Supplier of CookieHandler. Invocation of the Supplier.get() returns actual value of the property. The value provided must be fully qualified name of a DefaultHttpCookieManagerProperty.CookieManagerSupplier subclass.
